{
  "texts": [
    "1 ⃝, 2 ⃝, and 3 ⃝ show the sequence of each step in the DFT operation.",
    "(c) introduces the details of the Earth-Adapter component structures.",
    "3}, parameterized by ϵ, to represent the three adapter experts.",
    "For the network architecture, we adopt the framework introduced by Rein (Wei et al. 2024), integrating DINOv2-L (Oquab et al.",
    "2023) as the backbone, represented as f ϕ and parameterized by ϕ, alongside Mask2Former (Cheng et al. 2022) as the decoder, denoted by f θ and parameterized by θ."
  ]
}